I think he may be referring to the fact that under &quot;View unread posts&quot;, if you click on the <strong>post subject/thread name itself</strong> it does not mark the thread as read -- instead, you have to click on the last page number shown under the post subject/thread name to get that to happen.  (Or in the case there's been multiple pages of posts since your last visit, you have to visit all of them, if I remember right)<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=3">koitsu</a> — Sun Jan 13, 2013 2:38 pm</p><hr />
